  "body": "View this post on the web at https://www.lennysnewsletter.com/p/snapchat-ceo-why-distribution-is\r\n\r\nEvan Spiegel, the co-founder and CEO of Snap, is one of the very few people in the world who has successfully built and scaled a lasting consumer social product. Snapchat has nearly 1 billion MAUs, and Evan and his team invented some of the most important consumer products and features, including Stories, AR glasses, swipe-based navigation, the camera as the primary UX, and a lot more.\r\nListen on YouTube [ https://substack.com/redirect/14689af9-ccb4-4181-a53c-5ca4acf2217b?j=eyJ1IjoiMWllZnkifQ.sG3OqnkHDNZpplC0eLA9u0NYhAE4J8yHwSPDyeVA8k8 ], Spotify [ https://substack.com/redirect/d8569481-6627-41b6-8402-661c4e9ce49e?j=eyJ1IjoiMWllZnkifQ.sG3OqnkHDNZpplC0eLA9u0NYhAE4J8yHwSPDyeVA8k8 ], and Apple Podcasts [ https://substack.com/redirect/e298c5ed-78a3-40c9-a83c-f6844e0700a2?j=eyJ1IjoiMWllZnkifQ.sG3OqnkHDNZpplC0eLA9u0NYhAE4J8yHwSPDyeVA8k8 ]\r\nIn our in-depth conversation, we discuss:\r\nWhy distribution is now the biggest challenge for creating a consumer technology business\r\nHow Snap innovates at scale with a 9-to-12-person design team: no titles, no hierarchy, hundreds of ideas reviewed weekly with the CEO\r\nWhy a pure software business is no longer a moat, and what actually creates durable competitive advantages today\r\nHow AI is changing the way designers work and why they’re now shipping code\r\nWhy every major Snap feature was copied and how that forced the company to work differently\r\nEvan’s prediction that humanity’s comfort with AI will be a bigger bottleneck than the technology itself\r\nThis year’s crucible moment for Snap\r\nBrought to you by:\r\nWorkOS [ https://substack.com/redirect/4fcf2d1a-cc05-4c0e-b956-9df813dd9f59?j=eyJ1IjoiMWllZnkifQ.sG3OqnkHDNZpplC0eLA9u0NYhAE4J8yHwSPDyeVA8k8 ]—Modern identity platform for B2B SaaS, free up to 1 million MAUs\r\nVanta [ https://substack.com/redirect/b48731ea-a135-4e48-9156-7984a9fda9ae?j=eyJ1IjoiMWllZnkifQ.sG3OqnkHDNZpplC0eLA9u0NYhAE4J8yHwSPDyeVA8k8 ]—Automate compliance, manage risk, and accelerate trust with AI\r\nWhere to find Evan Spiegel:\r\n• X: https://x.com/evanspiegel [ https://substack.com/redirect/54e97a39-0ca2-4807-80f0-8c27f8909549?j=eyJ1IjoiMWllZnkifQ.sG3OqnkHDNZpplC0eLA9u0NYhAE4J8yHwSPDyeVA8k8 ]\r\n• Snapchat: https://www.snapchat.com/@evan [ https://substack.com/redirect/67caafb9-088e-4509-830c-3f1e4be14ca2?j=eyJ1IjoiMWllZnkifQ.sG3OqnkHDNZpplC0eLA9u0NYhAE4J8yHwSPDyeVA8k8 ]\r\n• LinkedIn: https://www.linkedin.com/in/evan-spiegel [ https://substack.com/redirect/f039bed2-05f1-424a-8b9f-a8a3e0379806?j=eyJ1IjoiMWllZnkifQ.sG3OqnkHDNZpplC0eLA9u0NYhAE4J8yHwSPDyeVA8k8 ]\r\n• Website: https://www.spiegelfamilyfund.com [ https://substack.com/redirect/e4de9186-ad47-47cd-9936-2a30b4183436?j=eyJ1IjoiMWllZnkifQ.sG3OqnkHDNZpplC0eLA9u0NYhAE4J8yHwSPDyeVA8k8 ]\r\nReferenced:\r\n• Snapchat: https://www.snapchat.com [ https://substack.com/redirect/e109449d-74c4-45f8-a540-dfd39cc43a4c?j=eyJ1IjoiMWllZnkifQ.sG3OqnkHDNZpplC0eLA9u0NYhAE4J8yHwSPDyeVA8k8 ]\r\n• TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com [ https://substack.com/redirect/1db6ed09-b043-4b27-8f82-235741c0d5cf?j=eyJ1IjoiMWllZnkifQ.sG3OqnkHDNZpplC0eLA9u0NYhAE4J8yHwSPDyeVA8k8 ]\r\n• Threads: https://www.threads.com [ https://substack.com/redirect/33dbe22c-9922-4c4d-941b-f3d286c658cc?j=eyJ1IjoiMWllZnkifQ.sG3OqnkHDNZpplC0eLA9u0NYhAE4J8yHwSPDyeVA8k8 ]\r\n• Snapchat+: https://www.snapchat.com/plus [ https://substack.com/redirect/0ba4141b-bea7-4f40-9c07-e15d7ff74f39?j=eyJ1IjoiMWllZnkifQ.sG3OqnkHDNZpplC0eLA9u0NYhAE4J8yHwSPDyeVA8k8 ]\r\n• Instagram Plus: https://help.instagram.com/26266751476298047 [ https://substack.com/redirect/7f17104a-3eb0-4f5e-9005-cfee5ec8ccb5?j=eyJ1IjoiMWllZnkifQ.sG3OqnkHDNZpplC0eLA9u0NYhAE4J8yHwSPDyeVA8k8 ]\r\n• Pixy: https://www.pixy.com [ https://substack.com/redirect/778649a4-79d9-4d0a-b802-ab686ea4a988?j=eyJ1IjoiMWllZnkifQ.sG3OqnkHDNZpplC0eLA9u0NYhAE4J8yHwSPDyeVA8k8 ]\r\n• Specs: https://newsroom.snap.c