snewsletter.com/p/superhumans-secret-to-success-rahul-vohra [ https://substack.com/redirect/e0ea2ec6-d555-4e7f-ac97-caa8f2a53710?j=eyJ1IjoiMWllZnkifQ.sG3OqnkHDNZpplC0eLA9u0NYhAE4J8yHwSPDyeVA8k8 ]\r\n• Bobcat tractors: https://www.bobcat.com/na/en/equipment/tractors [ https://substack.com/redirect/aa359c86-fba5-4a9e-89e8-9e8682c6d4b4?j=eyJ1IjoiMWllZnkifQ.sG3OqnkHDNZpplC0eLA9u0NYhAE4J8yHwSPDyeVA8k8 ]\r\n• Palmer Luckey’s blog: https://palmerluckey.com [ https://substack.com/redirect/b3b7bd16-0d73-413c-8c6c-be1d03169b00?j=eyJ1IjoiMWllZnkifQ.sG3OqnkHDNZpplC0eLA9u0NYhAE4J8yHwSPDyeVA8k8 ]\r\n• ModRetro: https://modretro.com [ https://substack.com/redirect/f1fa681b-6731-4759-beb0-db24e1aca690?j=eyJ1IjoiMWllZnkifQ.sG3OqnkHDNZpplC0eLA9u0NYhAE4J8yHwSPDyeVA8k8 ]\r\n• Glean: https://www.glean.com [ https://substack.com/redirect/e8c36225-ad7c-492e-8925-6ee909136ad4?j=eyJ1IjoiMWllZnkifQ.sG3OqnkHDNZpplC0eLA9u0NYhAE4J8yHwSPDyeVA8k8 ]\r\n• Marty Supreme on Prime Video: https://www.primevideo.com/detail/Marty-Supreme/0GU3TFPDR9FE2C6L7AAWAA3QXD [ https://substack.com/redirect/b0d99d00-eb3d-4137-a459-aeaa7671367e?j=eyJ1IjoiMWllZnkifQ.sG3OqnkHDNZpplC0eLA9u0NYhAE4J8yHwSPDyeVA8k8 ]\r\n• Pokemon: https://www.pokemon.com [ https://substack.com/redirect/9a323405-2599-4f51-8342-0f91ac064323?j=eyJ1IjoiMWllZnkifQ.sG3OqnkHDNZpplC0eLA9u0NYhAE4J8yHwSPDyeVA8k8 ]\r\n• Puking rainbow lens: https://www.snapchat.com/lens/349f631e78cc4b3dbd8c9656a69dbdd0 [ https://substack.com/redirect/83fbbf58-b0df-4609-893a-3179c91df5af?j=eyJ1IjoiMWllZnkifQ.sG3OqnkHDNZpplC0eLA9u0NYhAE4J8yHwSPDyeVA8k8 ]\r\n• Face swap: https://www.snapchat.com/explore/face-swap [ https://substack.com/redirect/992025e3-bdc5-4bcc-9482-273248d22c00?j=eyJ1IjoiMWllZnkifQ.sG3OqnkHDNZpplC0eLA9u0NYhAE4J8yHwSPDyeVA8k8 ]\r\nRecommended books:\r\n• Loonshots: How to Nurture the Crazy Ideas That Win Wars, Cure Diseases, and Transform Industries: https://www.amazon.com/Loonshots-Nurture-Diseases-Transform-Industries/dp/1250185963 [ https://substack.com/redirect/3c8a15e7-0e36-41ba-a3a7-5b0a7743bbcd?j=eyJ1IjoiMWllZnkifQ.sG3OqnkHDNZpplC0eLA9u0NYhAE4J8yHwSPDyeVA8k8 ]\r\n • Thinking, Fast and Slow: https://www.amazon.com/Thinking-Fast-Slow-Daniel-Kahneman/dp/0374533555 [ https://substack.com/redirect/298f7662-bece-442f-9efe-20c44b5a9d6d?j=eyJ1IjoiMWllZnkifQ.sG3OqnkHDNZpplC0eLA9u0NYhAE4J8yHwSPDyeVA8k8 ]\r\n• Apple: The First 50 Years: https://www.amazon.com/Apple-First-Years-David-Pogue/dp/1982134593 [ https://substack.com/redirect/ff1e6787-f845-4e68-9ee0-5b259900c889?j=eyJ1IjoiMWllZnkifQ.sG3OqnkHDNZpplC0eLA9u0NYhAE4J8yHwSPDyeVA8k8 ]\r\n• The End of the World Is Just the Beginning: Mapping the Collapse of Globalization―Irreverent Predictions from a Geopolitical Strategist: https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09CS8FRRD [ https://substack.com/redirect/69ba4492-8897-4a77-b366-469c2e2d3a80?j=eyJ1IjoiMWllZnkifQ.sG3OqnkHDNZpplC0eLA9u0NYhAE4J8yHwSPDyeVA8k8 ]\r\nProduction and marketing by https://penname.co/ [ https://substack.com/redirect/93087bed-fa3f-4b19-ad30-f0f7539e4f96?j=eyJ1IjoiMWllZnkifQ.sG3OqnkHDNZpplC0eLA9u0NYhAE4J8yHwSPDyeVA8k8 ]. For inquiries about sponsoring the podcast, email podcast@lennyrachitsky.com [ mailto:podcast@lennyrachitsky.com ].\r\nLenny may be an investor in the companies discussed.\r\nMy biggest takeaways from this conversation:...\r\n\r\nUnsubscribe https://substack.com/redirect/2/eyJlIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubGVubnlzbmV3c2xldHRlci5jb20vYWN0aW9uL2Rpc2FibGVfZW1haWw_.rOMoWXKTIOj5cAycqck0V9iAIXJFtt9epMbjC5F8FwA?",
